					<description><![CDATA[<div style="margin: 5px 5% 10px 5%;"><img src="https://gaminggadgets.de/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/ps3-metal-gear-solid-5.jpg" width="1024" height="576" title="Eine alte PS3 in neuem Glanz. (Foto: ruliweb)" alt="Eine alte PS3 in neuem Glanz. (Foto: ruliweb)" /></div>
